sequenceDiagram

participant User
participant Browser
participant AzureAD as Azure AD / Entra ID
participant MFA
participant App as SaaS Application
participant Token as Identity Token Service

Note over User,AzureAD: User Login Flow

User->>Browser: Open Enterprise Application
Browser->>App: Request Access

App->>AzureAD: Redirect to Identity Provider

AzureAD->>User: Request Credentials
User->>AzureAD: Enter Username + Password

AzureAD->>MFA: Trigger MFA Challenge
MFA->>User: Push Notification / OTP

User->>MFA: Approve Authentication
MFA->>AzureAD: MFA Verified

Note over AzureAD,Token: Token Issuance

AzureAD->>Token: Generate Identity Token
Token->>Browser: Return SAML / OIDC Token

Browser->>App: Present Authentication Token

App->>App: Validate Token Signature

App->>User: Grant Access (SSO)
